<dd>(The <i>Wrightspeed X1</i> is a <a href="/wiki/Electric_car" title="Electric car">electric car</a> utilising an Ariel Atom chassis, an <a href="/wiki/AC_Propulsion" title="AC Propulsion">AC Propulsion</a> motor, and <a href="/wiki/Lithium-Ion" title="Lithium-Ion" class="mw-redirect">Lithium-Ion</a> batteries).</dd>
